;; ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
;; Integration: VS Code
;; Explicit VS Code desktop/editor support for workflows that want to launch
;; Visual Studio Code from inside the sandbox, including Claude editor handoff.
;; Source: 55-integrations-optional/vscode.sb
;; $$require=65-apps/vscode-app.sb$$
;; ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

;; This integration is intentionally opt-in.
;;
;; Why:
;; - Not every Claude Code run needs or wants desktop VS Code access.
;; - The Claude editor handoff shim should only activate when the caller
;;   explicitly enables VS Code support with --enable=vscode.
;;
;; The actual app bundle, Electron, and persistence allowances are provided by
;; the required 65-apps/vscode-app.sb profile.
